import './App.css'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Header from './components/common/heading/Header'
import Home from './components/home/Home'

/*switch is now routes*/
function App(){
  return(
    <>
      <Router>
        <Header/> 
        <Routes>
          <Route path='/' element={<Home/>}/>
        </Routes>
      </Router>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
